text: You're back! So, do you have what you need?

Not enough to do the whole renovation, huh? 
 That's okay. I figured it would take some time.

In that case, let's just do it bit by bit! 
 It'll probably be better for me to gain some confidence 
 over time rather than all at once, anyways.
Oh, wow! I can already feel the difference!
I feel stronger now! A bit more confident, too.

You really are good at this! 
 Why's a homebuilder of your level working for free?
You just got your license? Could've fooled me!

Still, I guess it makes sense. 
 Fixing me up is a good way to get your name out there.

Thanks, though. Even if you get something out of it too, 
 I'm really grateful you're helping me like this.
